{"tid":1801222,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和你shop新辦法","createTime":"2019-12-28T12:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T12:45:21.000Z","uid":342419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a2cd49cdabdd9018e0db76e5ff3239018cbe4242","tid":1801222,"uid":342419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:41:44.000Z","msg":"依幾日班狗發瘋狗症<br />\n三七二一都打都拉<br />\n雖然一直都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原因係我地已經話曬地點俾佢地<br />\n俾曬時間佢放班便衣，防暴<br />\n但我地唔預先講又聚唔到人。<br />\n係兩難局面之下我諗到個辦法，<br />\n就係運用四兩撥千斤。<br />\n就以CWB為例，<br />\n和利shop地點係時代，<br />\n但行緊嘅同時，<br />\n搵人打電話，<br />\n話希慎有黑衣人，要求救。<br />\n你覺得佢地會唔會去希慎，從而分薄左時代嘅狗？"},{"pid":"98d29252b7e52d51659dff18c9f6b0b5932454b5","tid":1801222,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T12:42:25.000Z","msg":"－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=02ec1ccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n<br />\n【最後4日】全民票選十八區區議會主席與發言人－民主統戰部<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800922\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800922</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phk5doO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fphk5doO.jpg&h=40b71bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNVuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=02ec1ccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n快啲入黎投票呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmo